<tal:root
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  omit-tag="">

<div class="portlet" id="portlet-details">
  <h2>Further information</h2>
  <div class="portletBody portletContent">

    <img src="/@@/info" />
    When you register a project in Launchpad, you get the ability to manage
    the project. Later on, you can pass that permission on to someone else
    if, for example, the leader of the project development effort wants to
    manage it personally.

  </div>
</div>
</tal:root>
